Ability Scores:
Strength: Modifies melee attack, melee damage.
Dexterity: Modifies ranged attack, ranged damage, AC.
Constitution: Modifies HP total.
Intelligence: Modifies spell damage and spell saves.

Rest of the stats:
Level: Improves unit effectiveness.
Hit Die: Determines how much HP a unit has.
Initiative: Modifies initiative roll.
Speed: Determines how many squares a unit can move in its turn.
AC: Determines how hard the unit is to hit.
Base Attack Bonus: Modifies attack rolls.
Special Qualities: Determined at unit creation.

